{"tid":729950,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"健康台=中醫R生意台","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T04:43:37.000Z","uid":4880,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"028d1caf01ea008f68a8e3494123b5230987e48d","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:05:39.000Z","msg":"natural selection <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870153404478467937ff75432d9834338ddb2d93","tid":729950,"uid":27359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾巫醫死全家"},{"pid":"53cb19c063bb34e725e25a61e2d754b5f3aa070b","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"冇人睇個post就自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c790c93cae43aa62becb1d7d15e679e29b538","tid":729950,"uid":4037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"無實力既中醫咪上來呃客囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最容易呃就係皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢鋪fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625dcce346260f8fac06b745bb7b6ddaeec9218d","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd0c790c93cae43aa62becb1d7d15e679e29b538","tid":729950,"uid":4037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"無實力既中醫咪上來呃客囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最容易呃就係皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢鋪fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet