 /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[求救 ]手腕痛左差唔多2年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bovCrS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bovCrS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"DDE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26df0082cb196b2a144b3f35024da70debdcb117","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133613_c585cd98997aa3d87a26cf0d159aec80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133613_c585cd98997aa3d87a26cf0d159aec80.png&h=8046b197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塞錢入你袋系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648b88dac46a11aad15ff68b808fd995a1fb95b6","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"me 埃及醫生, 你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.egyptprivatetourguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/Ancient-Egyptian-medical-papyri-reveal-a-lot-of-about-medicine.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.egyptprivatetourguide.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2FAncient-Egyptian-medical-papyri-reveal-a-lot-of-about-medicine.jpg&h=b6b5e2ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a8e964dfd730afc72144d69768889fec61a7e7e","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/133953_c585cd98997aa3d87a26cf0d159aec80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F133953_c585cd98997aa3d87a26cf0d159aec80.png&h=3235d357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不相伯仲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🔫"},{"pid":"45959c1f5b0fc470ae70de3a0241b0e73cb49972","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陣間又有野睇"},{"pid":"babb9e3591839ad1de0404174a5a063a86538a6f","tid":729950,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"我睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/170537_05d00c37db254ddf0c765810a883a0f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F170537_05d00c37db254ddf0c765810a883a0f4.png&h=bbc96079&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4d54db9bab3ab4bf408a958be381754577e8171","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babb9e3591839ad1de0404174a5a063a86538a6f","tid":729950,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"我睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/170537_05d00c37db254ddf0c765810a883a0f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F170537_05d00c37db254ddf0c765810a883a0f4.png&h=bbc96079&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"乜乜ge乜乜通常都係知自己冇料, 叨下人地光"},{"pid":"b18e57ffb5c5b38afb2a2f72d46c0cbce4f4b8ae","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/183055_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F183055_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png&h=8905d842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到果位係連登sell中醫好落力果位出左篇咁ge文<br />\n篇野factual ge 問題之後再講<br />\n<br />\nyear1 都會學到點解寫文要加reference <br />\n<img src=\"https://lgimages.s3.amazonaws.com/data/imagemanager/22346/whycite_1152x864.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flgimages.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fdata%2Fimagemanager%2F22346%2Fwhycite_1152x864.png&h=85e273b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中你個tertiary source 就係好多份papers combine埋一齊 (好似textbook 同 monograph.)<br />\n而係呢篇文最重要ge係<br />\n1. 佢所講ge information 係咪一個事實<br />\n2. 究竟個source 入面講D乜<br />\n3. 佢cite 果份野係咪同你講ge野一樣 (e.g. 鑽石能力水係有research support, 不過份野講ge唔係部機囉.)"},{"pid":"d20c4ec821c3361f57621e487b35373198f595e2","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"1. Reference<br />\n<br />\n由ref.開始睇起, 次序不先後<br />\n<br />\n第一份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/184753_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F184753_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png&h=4c35dec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者叫Julie Deardorff, 但係我係佢個網搵唔到佢個biography <br />\n所以我就上左linkedin睇佢有D乜野學歷背景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/185215_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F185215_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png&h=12a7bd83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當一份tertiary source 冇cite 返D information, 究竟份source 可唔可信?<br />\n<br />\ntitle 就話<br />\nFood allergies not tied to eczema for most<br />\n<br />\n但係佢篇野入面就話<br />\n<br />\n&quot;For about one-third of eczema patients, specific foods &mdash; dairy, eggs, soy, wheat, peanuts, tree nuts and fish &mdash; can trigger flare-ups....&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁即係想點?<br />\n<br />\n去到篇野最後佢畀左兩個management method<br />\n1.Bathe in bleach.<br />\n<br />\n2.Try wet wrap therapy. <br />\n<br />\n成篇野steroid 只係提過一次你就想人浸漂白水? 世界咁大我識碌柒咩, 即刻上PubMed 搵下資料學下野先<br />\n<br />\nKeywords : (bleach AND eczema)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/190218_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F190218_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png&h=e06a0e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/190414_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F190414_c99985788f060c56d24a6d9bf66fdb7d.png&h=92b7ecdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nwet dressing 係有效ge, 不過想知多D就自己睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.schn.health.nsw.gov.au/fact-sheets/eczema-wet-dressing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schn.health.nsw.gov.au%2Ffact-sheets%2Feczema-wet-dressing&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ced00f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.schn.health.nsw.gov.au/fact-sheets/eczema-wet-dressing</a>"},{"pid":"3b76d2a4e314bc07d557f8782ab0366d8cc05cb7","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"第二份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nationaleczema.org/food-and-environmental-allergies-cause-eczema/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnationaleczema.org%2Ffood-and-environmental-allergies-cause-eczema%2F&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=61ff8244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nationaleczema.org/food-and-environmental-allergies-cause-eczema/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/191112_712a5db77d6590039909032d50cd373b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F191112_712a5db77d6590039909032d50cd373b.png&h=7da7cb7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一篇由醫生寫ge, 而且個org. 仲係national. 咁篇野到寫D乜?<br />\n<br />\n&quot;...Food allergies do exist and although in some the symptoms can be severe and even life threatening, in others the symptoms may be more mild and include worsening of eczema...&quot;<br />\n<br />\ntl;dr 我都冇睇曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過個醫生點睇?<br />\n<br />\nIn summary, while<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> food and environmental allergies really can play a role in eczema, they don&rsquo;t generally cause the condition</span></strong>. And diagnosing allergies, particularly food allergies, can be problematic. You need to take a multifaceted approach to eczema. It takes work to control this condition."},{"pid":"56d5d08e3f8bdd8afe64c7eb4d9b20de0f70a6fc","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:27:22.000Z","msg":"第三份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dietvsdisease.org/diet-eczema-treatment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dietvsdisease.org%2Fdiet-eczema-treatment%2F&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ff57a0ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dietvsdisease.org/diet-eczema-treatment/</a><br />\n<br />\n由一team nutritionists (佢地自己claim係) 寫的<br />\n<br />\n&quot;...Studies suggest the connection between childhood food allergy and eczema is 33 to 63%. Adult onset eczema is less likely linked with food allergy at a rate of 10%. However, this does not mean that food allergies cause eczema (10, 11)....&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而CD 我打算講完ref.之後再講<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Celiac Disease and Eczema<br />\nThose with celiac disease (CD) are 3 times more likely to suffer from eczema (17).<br />\n<br />\nEven relatives of those with CD are twice as likely to have eczema. This connection is based on the possible role of autoimmunity causing eczema (18).&quot;"},{"pid":"16ea7f1314bda987f11ff3e91371be6eef10c320","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"第4份 WebMD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/193039_d80ca45053e86a380d9332867bda5b05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F193039_d80ca45053e86a380d9332867bda5b05.png&h=93d36d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係google大學畢業。"},{"pid":"7642b6c244c6f4af01121a89659edb622cba10da","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"第五份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodallergy.org/about-fare/blog/new-research-on-food-allergies-and-atopic-dermatitis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodallergy.org%2Fabout-fare%2Fblog%2Fnew-research-on-food-allergies-and-atopic-dermatitis&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=87f9e4de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodallergy.org/about-fare/blog/new-research-on-food-allergies-and-atopic-dermatitis</a><br />\n<br />\n份野又quote左幾份studies<br />\n<br />\n &quot;...Exposure to a food allergen via ingestion can cause both IgE-mediated (or immediate) reactions and non-IgE-mediated (or delayed type) reactions, such as an exacerbation of eczema that typically occurs 6 to 48 hours after ingestion....&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而到篇文後面又講到<br />\n<br />\n&quot;...early introduction and regular consumption of peanuts decreased the development of peanut allergy among atopic children....&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁我又好好奇想知佢呢份野係嗡乜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa1414850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa1414850&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f8c73a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa1414850</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Conclusion<br />\nThe early introduction of peanuts significantly decreased the frequency of the development of peanut allergy among children at high risk for this allergy and modulated immune responses to peanuts. &quot;<br />\n<br />\ntl dr, 我亦都唔打算去assess 篇野ge quality<br />\n<br />\n不過重點係<br />\n篇野係想知early introduction 去decreased the development of peanut allergy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1a22cd944e7bd179f115e7633e5344d43014b5","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"第六份 係ncbi搵返黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5122280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5122280%2F&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6dc5f7ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5122280/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/195351_89335711c455967590a850a87ff28d6b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F195351_89335711c455967590a850a87ff28d6b.png&h=37ee8b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己睇我唔撚講"},{"pid":"c1d63a1f4f422c1d8a6d0cc5c0fb68f8506c5068","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"再開過個post 算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8688f258be716fc67bb486c6aeeb8ab1412bc0","tid":729950,"uid":166749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"好同意！我個frd 真係睇網上打手介紹d中醫而放棄佢婦科建議食西藥控制，點知越食中藥越衰，搞到個瘤爆大而要emergency做手術，慘慘豬"},{"pid":"5df930d601a28f9149713273c698a43603e3ee68","tid":729950,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim